<template>

  <!--底部导航-->
  <yd-tabbar :fixed="true">
    <yd-tabbar-item
      title="首页"
      link="#"
      v-on:click.native="onPressPush('main')"
      active
    >
      <yd-icon name="home" slot="icon" size="0.54rem"></yd-icon>
    </yd-tabbar-item>
    <yd-tabbar-item
      title="二手交易"
      link="#"
      v-on:click.native="onPressPush('ershou')"
    >
      <yd-icon name="shopcart-outline" slot="icon" size="0.54rem"></yd-icon>
    </yd-tabbar-item>
    <yd-tabbar-item title="兼职招聘" link="#">
      <yd-icon name="order" slot="icon" size="0.54rem"></yd-icon>
    </yd-tabbar-item>
    <yd-tabbar-item title="校园资讯" link="#">
      <yd-icon name="discover" slot="icon" size="0.54rem"></yd-icon>
    </yd-tabbar-item>
    <yd-tabbar-item title="个人中心" link="#">
      <yd-icon name="ucenter-outline" slot="icon" size="0.54rem"></yd-icon>
    </yd-tabbar-item>
  </yd-tabbar>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'bottom',
  methods: {
    onPressPush(route, params = {}) {
      this.$pushRoute(route, params);
    }
  }
};
</script>

<style scoped>
.footer {
  height: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
  padding-top: 0.3rem;
  text-align: center;
}
</style>
